# Dedicated .dockerignore for the NodeJS test container.
# Docker 20.10+ uses <Dockerfile>.dockerignore when -f is specified,
# so this takes precedence over the root .dockerignore.
# Build context is the repository root.
**
!Topaz.Tests.NodeJS/package.json
!Topaz.Tests.NodeJS/package-lock.json
!Topaz.Tests.NodeJS/smoke-service-bus.mjs
!Topaz.Tests.NodeJS/smoke-event-hub.mjs
